{"tid":1790980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以比個機會我地！！！","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T16:46:44.000Z","uid":29359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd693e94492108644950351e934320ff1a216a57","tid":1790980,"uid":29359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又做標題黨！<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n香港的社會問題隨處可見。面對社會的問題，<br />\n我們除了<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「表示令人擔心」</span></span></strong>之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，難道我們真的只能任人魚肉嗎？  我們團隊的編導及攝影- 一葉，從小關心時事，熱愛電影。<br />\n<br />\n今年的二月一葉拍攝了作品《歡樂時光》，講述生活在繁榮的香港，每個人都為生活馬不停蹄地奔波著，同樣片刻不敢停的阿誠，居無定所，每晚寄宿於網吧，省下開銷，努力為分隔兩地的妻女拼砌一個家，盼望早日一家團聚，然而平凡的願望在香港卻是遙不可及的夢。期間更拍攝到當時反對修訂條例大遊行的宣傳活動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2019:夏日宣言｜The Edge of Liberty｜《歡樂時光》片段</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rhcBwuIgv7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrhcBwuIgv7w&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=c2eb7185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rhcBwuIgv7w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在《2019：夏日宣言》尚餘大量後期工作以及訪問拍攝有待完成。 我們衷心希望《2019：夏日宣言》可以好好紀錄香港人堅毅不屈的精神以及反送中運動的核心價值。 希望大家可以幫助我們讓記錄片順利出世。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Please support us: 眾籌 (GoGetFunding) link:</span> </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><a href=\"http://www.theedgeofliberty.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theedgeofliberty.com&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=00b63a92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.theedgeofliberty.com</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftheedgeofliberty%2F&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=6c003ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/</a> <br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/edgeoflibertyhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fedgeoflibertyhk&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5ee2418f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitter.com/edgeoflibertyhk</a> <br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/theedgeofliberty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftheedgeofliberty&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0b401179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/theedgeofliberty</a> <br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/teol_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fteol_hk%2F&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=b7acb4fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/teol_hk/</a>"},{"pid":"4af50146d84adc3600ce9a225318ad7495b0b54c","tid":1790980,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e3b4bacaf80d6811b549fbbae5ab192d6e5bef3","tid":1790980,"uid":29359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dc1922495571edfab301a7fd3fe45290005c8a9","tid":1790980,"uid":29359,"like":0,"dis